nodes.name: features_extractor
nodes.class_name:
MultiAgentSelfAttentionExtractor(
  (agent_encoder): Sequential(
    (0): Linear(in_features=30, out_features=128, bias=True)
    (1): ReLU()
    (2): Linear(in_features=128, out_features=128, bias=True)
    (3): ReLU()
    (4): Linear(in_features=128, out_features=64, bias=True)
    (5): ReLU()
  )
  (query_proj): Linear(in_features=64, out_features=64, bias=True)
  (key_proj): Linear(in_features=64, out_features=64, bias=True)
  (value_proj): Linear(in_features=64, out_features=64, bias=True)
  (aggregator): Sequential(
    (0): Linear(in_features=256, out_features=32, bias=True)
    (1): ReLU()
    (2): Linear(in_features=32, out_features=32, bias=True)
    (3): ReLU()
  )
)

nodes.name: mlp_extractor
nodes.class_name:
MlpExtractor(
  (policy_net): Sequential(
    (0): Linear(in_features=32, out_features=64, bias=True)
    (1): Tanh()
    (2): Linear(in_features=64, out_features=64, bias=True)
    (3): Tanh()
  )
  (value_net): Sequential(
    (0): Linear(in_features=32, out_features=64, bias=True)
    (1): Tanh()
    (2): Linear(in_features=64, out_features=64, bias=True)
    (3): Tanh()
  )
)
